    <div class="faq-a" id="is-seo-replaced-by-ai"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>AI is changing how search results look, not what makes a page rankable. AI Overviews and chat-based search still cite the same pages that rank in traditional search. The pages they cite tend to be fast, structured, and authoritative. If your code passes the technical SEO checklist, your pages are eligible for AI citations. If it does not, you miss both the blue links and the AI surface.</p></div></div>
